  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.3.4">
<l>yārumōr nilaimaiya ṉeṉavaṟi variya vemperumāṉ</l>
<l>yārumōr nilaimaiya ṉeṉavaṟi veḷiyavem perumāṉ</l>
<l>pērumō rāyiram piṟapala vuṭaiyavem perumāṉ</l>
<l>pērumō ruruvamu muḷatillai yilatillai piṇakkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For anybody our lord is difficult to know as one of a single state.</l>
<l>For anybody our lord is easy to know as one of a single state.</l>
<l>A thousand names and many others possesses our lord.</l>
<l>[There is] a disagreement [as to whether] he is not one with name and form or whether he is not without.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
